{"tid":2455100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約時報中文網：「格言大家」毛澤東","createTime":"2021-03-20T19:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T06:45:36.000Z","uid":172349,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5bce32d64c786029c4d89c318f4622768f8290f2","tid":2455100,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:03:48.000Z","msg":"在中國，毛澤東思想是被寫進共產黨章程的指導方針、是中共官方學說的重要部分、是大紅色標語上的常見表述、也是大學生課堂的必修課程。而在中國以外，這位政治強人的思想和理論被稱為「毛主義」(Maoism)，一度在全球都有舉足輕重的影響力。<br />\n廣告<br />\n上週，時報發表了為歷史及文學教授藍詩玲(Julia Lovell)的新書《毛主義：一部全球史》(Maoism: A Global History)撰寫的書評，該書介紹了秘魯、印度尼西亞、非洲、東南亞、印度和尼泊爾等國的毛主義，並挖掘了毛主義在這些國家大受歡迎的原因。文中提到：<br />\n「加上他支持婦女平等，妙語不斷（『革命不是請客吃飯』；『帝國主義都是紙老虎』），以及驚人的理論文章產量，毛主義對20世紀革命者如此重要的原因也就顯而易見了。」<br />\n<br />\n「Throw in his support for women&rsquo;s equality, a penchant for quotable aphorisms (『revolution is not a dinner party&rsquo;; 『imperialism is a paper tiger&rsquo;) as well as a huge output of theoretical writings, and it becomes clear why Maoism was so important to 20th-century revolutionaries.」<br />\n根據劍橋詞典，aphorism的意思是「一句簡短但明智的話語，用於表達一般真相」(a short clever saying that is intended to express a general truth)，通常被翻譯為「格言、箴言」。該詞最早出現於16世紀早期，源於晚期拉丁語aphorismus，後者演變自希臘語aphorismos，意思是「定義」(definition)。<br />\n正如文章所寫，毛澤東的確是一位「格言大家」，我們耳熟能詳的許多句子都出自於他的文章或講話，比如「謙虛使人進步，驕傲使人落後」（這句話出自他在中共八大開幕式上的講話，演講稿由其秘書田家英撰寫。&mdash;&mdash;編著）、「為人民服務」、「哪裡有壓迫，哪裡就有反抗」。毛的許多名言還來源於他所作的詩詞，比如「一萬年太久，只爭朝夕」、「數風流人物，還看今朝」。<br />\n你還知道毛澤東的哪些格言？你最喜歡哪一句？歡迎與我們分享你的觀點，也歡迎對「每日一詞」這個欄目提出你的意見和建議。我們的讀者信箱地址是：cn.letters@nytimes.com。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/culture/20190911/wod-aphorism/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fculture%2F20190911%2Fwod-aphorism%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfRnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=f92c4c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/culture/20190911/wod-aphorism/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"0356bc25faf6de35349cb25d3e120a17cd614b6f","tid":2455100,"uid":265839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:05:07.000Z","msg":"Nytimes變環球時報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cce8864f1e66bfd737b54dbab5194368b061cc","tid":2455100,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0356bc25faf6de35349cb25d3e120a17cd614b6f","tid":2455100,"uid":265839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:05:07.000Z","msg":"Nytimes變環球時報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T19:16:44.000Z","msg":"NYTimes（已被收編）"},{"pid":"7700c64b5a89d090dc1ac52d9d0dd6bbf0163382","tid":2455100,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T21:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpOnpJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpOnpJ8.jpg&h=3622f0ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8c983a35a9316e2e360918ac8cb0b6ac1115109","tid":2455100,"uid":36901,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T21:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bkkhenr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbkkhenr.png&h=52672e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最愛呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7dd1df87b1a4f055dda37e75bd79bd2f2717f3","tid":2455100,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T21:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79de11208368ad1844c3b44734ee7eb976f34d41","tid":2455100,"uid":72730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T21:35:01.000Z","msg":"「我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。」<br />\n〈被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事〉，1939年5月26日<br />\n<br />\n「凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。」<br />\n〈和中央社、掃蕩報、新民報三記者的談話〉，1939年9月16日"},{"pid":"91f939354177cc5afc5c7429b228e8feb761d059","tid":2455100,"uid":91397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T22:11:01.000Z","msg":"舉著紅旗反紅旗<br />\n<br />\n槍桿子裏出政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d681d98b9f702efd548bb80ea0c2bfe00749dbd4","tid":2455100,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T22:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04gCASU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04gCASU.png&h=7034692d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2f6bfed193a06af8d80c7c98c984b8141c01e53","tid":2455100,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T22:27:21.000Z","msg":"敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追。"},{"pid":"e891f73b09d59dbf4159d52414b307d807f84749","tid":2455100,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T22:29:16.000Z","msg":"世界是你們的，也是我們的，但是歸根結底是你們的。你們年青人朝氣蓬勃，正在興旺時候，好像早晨八、九點鍾的太陽。希望寄托在你們身上。"},{"pid":"0c0a0f6cee87a4743521b54f0e97adbb075e9ba3","tid":2455100,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T22:34:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">打土豪、分田地！ </span></span>"},{"pid":"afee3f658e9094c0084f3dbebc4a40cdd0efdc21","tid":2455100,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T22:38:00.000Z","msg":"賀新郎&middot;讀史<br />\n1964年<br />\n<br />\n人猿相揖別。<br />\n只幾個石頭磨過，<br />\n小兒時節。<br />\n銅鐵爐中翻火焰，<br />\n為問何時猜得？<br />\n不過幾千寒熱。<br />\n人世難逢開口笑，<br />\n上疆場彼此彎弓月。<br />\n流遍了，<br />\n郊原血。<br />\n<br />\n一篇讀罷頭飛雪，<br />\n但記得斑斑點點，<br />\n幾行陳跡。<br />\n五帝三皇神聖事，<br />\n騙了無涯過客。<br />\n有多少風流人物？<br />\n盜蹠莊蹻流譽後，<br />\n更陳王奮起揮黃鉞。<br />\n歌未竟，<br />\n東方白。"},{"pid":"aa72359f38109fcaadb5218e7130fddaeb4040ce","tid":2455100,"uid":355748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"凡是要推翻一個政權，總要先造成輿論，總要先做意識形態方面的工作。不論革命、反革命，都是如此。"}]}